  • public class Collision
extends java.lang.Object
    Filename: Collision.java
    Author:
    dawsonheykoop Purpose: An instantiation of this represents the relationship between two objects, and more particularly their relative coordinates. It makes checking for a collision easier, so checking multiple times is unnecessary.
